      },
      {
        "chunk_type": "opening",
        "translations": {
          "en": "I heard a man ask Aba 'Abd Allah عليه السلام, and he said: “At times I urinate and cannot access water, and that becomes difficult for me.”",
          "ur": "",
          "tr": "",
          "fa": "",
          "id": "",
          "bn": "",
          "es": "",
          "fr": "",
          "de": "",
          "ru": "",
          "zh": ""
        },
        "word_start": 22,
        "word_end": 41
      },
      {
        "chunk_type": "body",
        "translations": {
          "en": "So he عليه السلام said: “When you urinate and wipe yourself, then wipe your male organ with your saliva. Then if you find something, say: this is from that.”",
